snippet.title: Tattoo Tycoon // HandyGames Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
#TattooTycoon #Ink #Simulation 

Become a tattoo artist and manage your own tattoo parlor. Find the perfect motifs for your curious customers and turn their vague wishes into amazing skin art. Grow from a small personal studio to a multi-parlor business over the different districts of Tattuga Bay.

#HandyGames #IndieGames #GermanPublisher
by http://www.handy-games.com. ▶
